Class TrackableCollection<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.bindroid.trackable.Trackable
      com.bindroid.trackable.TrackableCollection<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of object in the List.
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>
public class TrackableCollection<T>
extends Trackable
implements java.util.List<T>

A List implementation that implements Trackable on all of its methods, notifying Trackers whenever a change to the list occurs.
